great-north-bobs-burgers-loren-bouchard-1202140322/|title=Fox Orders New Animated Comedy From ''Bob\u2019s Burgers'' Creator Loren Bouchard|accessdate=14 May 2019}}</ref>\n\n===Casting===\nOn May 9, 2019, it was announced that [[Nick Offerman]], [[Jenny Slate]], [[Megan Mullally]], [[Will Forte]], [[Aparna Nancherla]], [[Paul Rust]], and [[Dulc\u00e9 Sloan]] have been cast in series regular roles. All but the latter two have either guest starred or have recurring roles on ''[[Bob's Burgers]]''.<ref name=\"SeriesOrder\"/>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Loren Bouchard}}\n{{FOXNetwork Shows (current and upcoming)}}\n{{Fox Animation}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Great North}}\n<!--[[Category:2020s American animated comedy television series]]\n[[Category:2020s American adult animated television series]]-->\n[[Category:American animated sitcoms]]\n[[Category:English-language television programs]]\n[[Category:Upcoming comedy television series]]\n[[Category:Upcoming animated television series]]\n[[Category:Television series by Fox Television Animation]]\n[[Category:Television series by 20th Century Fox Television]]\n[[Category:American adult animated comedy television series]]\n[[Category:Fox Broadcasting Company original programming]]\n[[Category:Television shows set in Alaska]]\n[[Category:Television series by Fox Entertainment]]\n\n{{US-animation-tv-prog-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox television\n| show_name                = The Great North\n| image                    = \n| genre                    = [[Animated sitcom]]\n| creator                  = Wendy Molyneux<br>Lizzie Molyneux<br>Minty Lewis\n| writer                   = \n| story                    = \n| voices                   = {{Plainlist|\n*[[Nick Offerman]]\n*[[Jenny Slate]]\n*[[Megan Mullally]]\n*[[Paul Rust]]\n*[[Aparna Nancherla]]\n*[[Will Forte]]\n*[[Dulc\u00e9 Sloan]]\n}}\n| composer                 = \n| country                  = United States\n| language                 = English\n| num_seasons              = <!--Only increment as a new season premieres, per the documentation of the template!-->\n| num_episodes             = <!--Only increment as a new episode premieres, per the documentation of the template!-->\n| list_episodes            = \n| executive_producer       = {{Plainlist|\n* [[Loren Bouchard]]\n* Wendy Molyneux\n* Lizzie Molyneux\n* Minty Lewis\n}}\n| producer                 = \n| editor                   = \n| runtime                  = \n| company                  = {{Plainlist|\n* [[Bento Box Entertainment]]\n* [[Fox Entertainment]]\n* [[20th Century Fox Television]]\n}}\n| distributor              = [[Fox Corporation]]<br>[[20th Television]]\n| network                  = [[Fox Broadcasting Company|Fox]]\n| picture_format           =\n| audio_format             =\n| first_aired              = <!--{{Start date|YYYY|MM|DD}}-->\n| last_aired               = <!--{{End date|present}}-->\n| website                  = \n| website_title            = \n}}\n\n'''The Great North''' is an upcoming American [[animated sitcom]] created by Wendy Molyneux, Lizzie Molyneux and Minty Lewis for the [[Fox Broadcasting Company]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2018/09/animated-alaska-set-family-comedy-from-bobs-burgers-trio-gets-fox-pilot-presentation-order-nick-offerman-jenny-slate-megan-mullally-1202473238/|title=Animated Alaska Set Family Comedy from Bob's Burgers trio get FOX pilot presentation|accessdate=14 October 2019}}</ref> \n\n==Premise==\n''The Great North'' takes place in Alaska, where a single dad, Beef Tobin, juggles his life keeping his kids close together, including being involved in his daughter's artistic dreams in the local mall.<ref>{{cite web|title=Fox Orders 6 New Series, Including A.I. And Fertility Doctor Dramas|url=https://shadowandact.com/fox-orders-6-new-series-including-sisters-next-prodigal-son|accessdate=14 May 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Cast==\n*[[Nick Offerman]] as Beef Tobin<ref name=\"SeriesOrder\">{{cite web|url=https://tvline.com/2019/05/09/new-fox-comedies-2019-nick-offerman-jason-biggs-sitcom/|title=Fox Orders Nick Offerman Cartoon, Jason Biggs Family Comedy to Series|accessdate=14 May 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Episodes==\n{{Episode table |background=#C9FFE5|overall=|title= |director= |writer= |airdate= |prodcode= |viewers= |country=U.S. |episodes=\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = \n| Title           = Sexi Moose Adventure (aka \"Pilot\")<ref name=\"Copy101\">{{cite web|url=https://cocatalog.loc.gov/cgi-bin/Pwebrecon.cgi?Search_Arg=PAu003947574&Search_Code=REGS|title=Catalog of Copyright Entries \"Sexi Moose Adventure\" ''The Great North''}}</ref>\n| DirectedBy      = \n| WrittenBy       = \n| OriginalAirDate = \n| ProdCode        = \n| Viewers         = \n| ShortSummary    = \n| LineColor       = #C9FFE5\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = \n| Title           = Romantic Meat-Based Adventure<ref name=\"Copy102\">{{cite web|url=https://cocatalog.loc.gov/cgi-bin/Pwebrecon.cgi?Search_Arg=PAu004007580&Search_Code=REGS|title=Catalog of Copyright Entries \"Romantic Meat-Based Adventure\" ''The Great North''}}</ref>\n| DirectedBy      = \n| WrittenBy       = \n| OriginalAirDate = \n| ProdCode        = 1LBW02<ref name=\"Copy102\" />\n| Viewers         = \n| ShortSummary    = \n| LineColor       = #C9FFE5\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   =\n| Title           = Feast of Not People Adventure<ref name=\"Copy103\">{{cite web|url=https://cocatalog.loc.gov/cgi-bin/Pwebrecon.cgi?Search_Arg=PAu004007582&Search_Code=REGS|title=Catalog of Copyright Entries \"Feast of Not People Adventure\" ''The Great North''}}</ref>\n| DirectedBy      = \n| WrittenBy       = \n| OriginalAirDate = \n| ProdCode        = 1LBW03<ref name=\"Copy103\" />\n| Viewers         = \n| ShortSummary    = \n| LineColor       = #C9FFE5\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = \n| Title           = Avocado Barter Adventure<ref name=\"Copy104\">{{cite web|url=https://cocatalog.loc.gov/cgi-bin/Pwebrecon.cgi?Search_Arg=PAu004007676&Search