marter-than-5th-grader-revivals-nickelodeon-2019-content-slate-1202557532/|title=\u2018SpongeBob\u2019 Spinoffs, \u2018All That\u2019 & \u2018Are You Smarter Than 5th Grader?\u2019 Revivals & More On Nickelodeon\u2019s 2019 Content Slate|website=Deadline|first=Denise|last=Petski|date=February 14, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Video: Nickelodeon Reveals Premiere Date and Trailer for Return of \"Are You Afraid of the Dark?\"|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/video/2019/09/13/video-nickelodeon-reveals-premiere-date-and-trailer-for-return-of-are-you-afraid-of-the-dark-290501/20190913nickelodeon01/|work=[[The Futon Critic]]|date=September 13, 2019}}</ref>\n\n{{Aired episodes|2019|10|25|title=Are You Afraid of the Dark?|finished=8}}\n\n==Series overview==\n<onlyinclude>{{Series overview\n| color1       = #9C2424\n| link1        = <includeonly>List of Are You Afraid of the Dark? episodes</includeonly>#Season 1 (1991\u201392)\n| episodes1    = 13\n| start1       = {{Start date|1991|10|25}}\n| end1         = {{End date|1992|11|21}}\n| network1     = [[YTV (TV channel)|YTV]]<br>[[Nickelodeon]]\n\n| color2       = #275292\n| link2        = <includeonly>List of Are You Afraid of the Dark? episodes</includeonly>#Season 2 (1993)\n| episodes2    = 13\n| start2       = {{Start date|1993|6|19}}\n| end2         = {{End date|1993|10|2}}\n\n| color3       = #216424\n| link3        = <includeonly>List of Are You Afraid of the Dark? episodes</includeonly>#Season 3 (1994)\n| episodes3    = 13\n| start3       = {{Start date|1994|1|8}}\n| end3         = {{End date|1994|4|16}}\n\n| color4       = #6F349C\n| link4        = <includeonly>List of Are You Afraid of the Dark? episodes</includeonly>#Season 4 (1994\u201395)\n| episodes4    = 13\n| start4       = {{Start date|1994|10|1}}\n| end4         = {{End date|1995|1|21}}\n\n| color5       = #23556C\n| link5        = <includeonly>List of Are You Afraid of the Dark? episodes</includeonly>#Season 5 (1995\u201396)\n| episodes5    = 13\n| start